      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:39:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟就应用程序发布发出最后通牒，TikTok 面临罚款风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-risks-fines-as-eu-issues-ultimatum-over-app-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周一启动新调查，调查字节跳动有限公司在未提供全面风险评估的情况下在法国和西班牙推出 TikTok Lite 应用程序时是否违反了欧盟的新内容法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-risks-fines-as-eu-issues-ultimatum-over-app-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:32:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪对穆斯林的评论引发向选举机构的投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/modi-s-comment-about-muslims-prompts-complaint-to-election-body</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度主要反对党在总理纳伦德拉·莫迪过去两天在集会上发表言论后，向该国选举机构提出投诉，称这些言论造成宗教分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/modi-s-comment-about-muslims-prompts-complaint-to-election-body</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于供应紧张迹象，糖价从近一年低点上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sugar-rises-from-near-one-year-low-on-signs-of-tighter-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约食糖期货上涨，因空头回补和供应紧张的迹象提振了上周价格跌至一年多以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sugar-rises-from-near-one-year-low-on-signs-of-tighter-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:14:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应紧张持续，铜价每吨达 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/copper-nears-10-000-as-investors-bet-on-rising-global-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价每吨接近 10,000 美元，创下两年新高，因为投资者继续押注矿商将难以满足对这种领头工业金属需求激增的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/copper-nears-10-000-as-investors-bet-on-rising-global-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
